1.2 Company profile

As a minority interest, Siemens Energy AG is not included in this Sustainability Report. Siemens is a technology company that operates in nearly all countries of the world. Ever since it was founded in 1847, Siemens has provided solutions to global challenges and stands for innovation, quality, and reliability. We are focused on leveraging the digital and sus- tainability transformation to drive sustainable growth.

